## 
### Nodejs
[Nodejs](http://www.runoob.com/nodejs/nodejs-install-setup.html)

c, `npm config ls -l` ,,  `; ...` ,

```bash

; cli configs
long = true
scope = ""
user-agent = "npm/4.0.5 node/v7.4.0 win32 x64"

; builtin config undefined
; prefix = "C:\\Users\\{userName}\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm" (overridden)


; cache = "C:\\Users\\{userName}\\AppData\\Roaming\\npm-cache" (overridden)
cache-lock-retries = 10
cache-lock-stale = 60000
cache-lock-wait = 10000
cache-max = null

```



```bash

npm config set cache "${NodejsHome}\node_cache" # ${NodejsHome}

npm config set prefix "${NodejsHome}"

```

`npm config set prefix`  `npm install -g xxx` (`Path`)

, [npm](http://npm.taobao.org/)

```bash

npm install -g cnpm --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org

```

,`npm install``cnpm install`

### Hexo

```bash

cd d:\blog # 

cnpm install hexo-cli -g # hexo

hexo init # (hexo init blog blog)

cnpm install # npm

hexo g # 

hexo s # ,http://localhost:4000/

```

 [http://localhost:4000/](http://localhost:4000/) blog

```bash

# 

hexo n == hexo new

hexo g == hexo generate

hexo s == hexo server

hexo d == hexo deploy

# 
hexo d -g # 

hexo s -g # 

```

windowsgit-bash.exe

### GitHub 

#### rsa

```bash

ssh-keygen

# 
Enter file in which to save the key (/c/Users/{userName}/.ssh/id_rsa): # rsakey,id_rsa
Enter passphrase (empty for no passphrase): # 
Enter same passphrase again: #

```

####  ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub 

```
ssh-rsa

xxxx key xxxxxx  userName@email

```

#### github ssh key

 ->settings->Personal settings->SSH and GPG keys->New SSH key->Title ->Key ssh-rsa ->Add SSH key

#### 

  + ->New repository->Repository name ${userName}.github.io ${userName}->Create repository

### github

#### github

```bash

git init # 

git add . # 

git commit -m '' # message

git checkout -b blog-source # , travis-ci 

git remote add origin git@github.com:${userName}/${userName}.github.io.git #   ${userName} 

git push origin blog-source:blog-source # github

```

####  `.travis.yml` 

```yml
language: node_js
node_js: stable

# S: Build Lifecycle
install:
  - npm install


before_script:
  - npm install hexo-helper-qrcode --save
  - npm install hexo-generator-feed --save

script:
  - hexo g

after_script:
  - cd ./public
  # ,CNAME
  - if [ $MY_DOMAIN ]; then echo ${MY_DOMAIN} > CNAME; fi 
  - git init
  - git config user.name "${userName}"
  - git config user.email "${email}"
  - git add .
  - git commit -m "Update docs"
  - git push --force --quiet "https://${GH_TOKEN}@${GH_REF}" master:master

branches:
  only:
    - blog-source
env:
 global:
   - GH_REF: github.com/${userName}/${userName}.github.io.git
   # 
   - MY_DOMAIN: anjia.ml
```

${userName}${email}
